    interviewQuestions: ['Why does transfer learning work even when source and target domains differ?', 'What strategies exist for deciding which layers to freeze vs. fine-tune?', 'How do you prevent catastrophic forgetting during transfer learning?', 'Compare transfer learning with multi-task learning.', 'When would transfer learning not be beneficial?'],
    commonMistakes: ['Using too high a learning rate aggressive fine-tuning destroys pre-trained features use a low learning rate.', 'Freezing too many layers if the target task differs from source more layers need fine-tuning.', 'Not considering source domain similarity using a text pre-trained model for image tasks provides minimal benefit.'],
